{"tid":1923961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[以史為鑑] 當年目擊8964嘅香港人點解最後冇罷到工??","createTime":"2020-03-13T11:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T18:36:42.000Z","uid":225100,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4777c99aad419e3f1a59d34e43f0e03d97534f","tid":1923961,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"先旨聲明<ins>唔係想分化責怪上一代人</ins><br />\n而係香港嘅局 大家既然唔會全民勇武就只得番全民極致和理非呢一條路<br />\n即係<span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span><br />\n而呢場三罷相信會係勝負關鍵<br />\n但中共港共冇可能綁住對手乜都唔做任我哋搞<br />\n<br />\n所以想各位史學家講講當年有咩因素令到罷工失敗 <span style=\"color: red;\">汲取教訓</span><br />\n當年司徒華領導嘅民主派諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622840ad532d8e78af2e013a32b49ec0ef11e97c","tid":1923961,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為你講我先入黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d6e0a239bf68ecc11715374735d4ce5766968c","tid":1923961,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"碧街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8849c5270e50ae965471a6519719f1c88e559a","tid":1923961,"uid":25240,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"因為司徒華係地下黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c7891ff196ce231ab4b566a4800b172cb173fc","tid":1923961,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4d6e0a239bf68ecc11715374735d4ce5766968c","tid":1923961,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"碧街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"係，應該關呢單事"},{"pid":"98b89e085a3615ef9f18efc69c7f1f5ae159b7f1","tid":1923961,"uid":225100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"btw希望大家唔好以係立會過半就等於贏咗 有幫助還有幫助 終歸是支線<br />\n我哋搞工會遲早都要黎場認實嘅大罷工<br />\n要令罷工成功唔易 所以事前先要準備多啲"},{"pid":"73503f329112c281e7b8cfb7594c237b3283887c","tid":1923961,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},{"pid":"f7186304097793a01cf9440cd0e5450d7ea24cb9","tid":1923961,"uid":31151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"罷工失敗原因得一個<br />\n就係共諜 司徒華"},{"pid":"eef7997e5a187ab171307f8f9e3a7e4823f893f4","tid":1923961,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"司徒華在1989年六四事件前一直與中國共產黨保持良好關係，1949年由中共地下黨人廖一原介紹下，加入新民主主義青年團，該團為共產主義青年團的前身。同時參與成立「學友中西舞蹈研究社」，後來改名為學友社。[22]1958年，司徒華雖然在幹事會改選中被排擠出學友社的領導層，但仍在其他有中國共產黨背景的團體中做義務工作，例如在《兒童報》擔任編輯。據司徒華自傳披露、其胞妹司徒嬋剖述，司徒華向曾在學友社與他意見不合的歐陽成潮主動要求加入中國共產黨，結果被拒 ，令他感被騙及遺棄，內心十分難受[23]。"},{"pid":"9cbca077470ac446c86af45442d3b510a8b7dd3b","tid":1923961,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622840ad532d8e78af2e013a32b49ec0ef11e97c","tid":1923961,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為你講我先入黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"sor 集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6859bee9544cdabd2a57ff32705cde27626f4645","tid":1923961,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"屍屠老狗仲盲信緊可以建設民主中國<br />\n感化共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\